WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.739
Hello, young word explorer.

2
00:00:01.739 --> 00:00:05.217
Welcome to Unit 9, Let's Explore the City!.

3
00:00:05.217 --> 00:00:09.565
This unit has 23 vocabulary cards in 4 learning groups.

4
00:00:09.565 --> 00:00:12.608
Group 1 is Places in the City.

5
00:00:12.608 --> 00:00:18.260
Listen for words such as library, shopping center, underground, ferry, Ferris wheel, market.

6
00:00:18.260 --> 00:00:21.739
Group 2 is City Sounds and Getting Around.

7
00:00:21.739 --> 00:00:26.956
Listen for words such as traffic, helicopter, bus, map, directions, straight ahead.

8
00:00:26.956 --> 00:00:29.130
Group 3 is Aquarium Animals.

9
00:00:29.130 --> 00:00:33.477
Listen for words such as aquarium, octopus, penguin, turtle, shark.

10
00:00:33.477 --> 00:00:36.086
Group 4 is Describing Words (Adjectives).

11
00:00:36.086 --> 00:00:40.868
Listen for words such as amazing, beautiful, clever, dangerous, huge, scary.

12
00:00:40.868 --> 00:00:51.738
For each word, listen and repeat, read five sentences, notice the word type, practise spelling, write your own sentence, and ask the tutor for help.

13
00:00:51.738 --> 00:00:54.781
You are ready to begin Unit 9.
